Dialogue: I did it... I won!
One last precaution...just in case.
Hmm? Is someone there?
...I'd better hurry.
I feel eyes on my back...
It's just my imagination.
Almost there. Let's get this over with!
I should be safe here.
The goods are in place. Now I just have to collect...
I don't know why you're following me, but I've no business with you.
So this is All Saints' Wake? Fascinating.
Inspiration for our own festivities, perhaps?
Yes, yes, food for thought indeed!
What wonderful decorations!
Quite so! Perhaps we could devise costumes to match?
I daresay this'll make a fine article!
I wonder if I've missed any other intriguing details...
This fellow seems rather suspect...
I better start workin' hard to put food on the table too...
Papa Gruff's the greatest clown around!
A pumpkin-themed menu might prove a hit with the customers.
Roll up, roll up! The show's about to start!
I've lost me coinpurse, you see...
\<pant> \<pant>
You win, mister!
Wow, you actually won!
I'm impressed!
Just you wait, I'll become even faster!
Thanks for playing with us!
I tell you, my man is such a worrier!
Forget about him! We're here to have fun!
So then I says to him...
Haha! Unbelievable.
Easy now. Take a deep breath.
Curse those mechanical bastards...
Are you hurt?
Oh gods, what's happening!?
Those sentries didn't seem to be malfunctioning. Which begs the question...
Are you okay?
I'll live. I think...
What did I do to deserve this!?
Count yourself lucky, you're still alive.
G-Gods... How much did I drink?
The mechanical soldiers are part of the army, right?
Wait, you're saying our own army attacked us!? Why!?

Keep it together!
Help's on its way!

Just hang in there.
You'll pull through!
I heard the sentries raided the eighth level too...
Sounds like the entire 'keep came under attack.
Mama? Maaamaaa!
My family... Are they safe?
\<groan>
Are you all right!?
All this wreckage...
I must...protect the people...
Mama! Papa! \<sob>
Where are you!?
What...what happened?
Why? What did we do to deserve this?
Help me! Help me!
Ugh...
Ghhh...
Who were those people...?
The next show's about to start!

You ever seen someone
with rhythm like that?

You heard the man.
Let's hurry inside!
The tickets are all sold out...
Ah, sheer bliss.
When is this match going to start...
The wait's driving me mad!
So, who's your favorite fighter?
So hard to choose.
Blue's pretty tasty too...
Hmmm.
Made your mind up yet?
Just give me a few more minutes!
Good thing the aetheryte made it through the storm in one piece.
My foot fell right through the damaged planks!
What can I get you?
Two whitefish tacos, please!
Coming right up.
Two whitefish!
Understood!
Up you go!
Hehehe!
These things are addictive...
Ahhh! Been waiting my whole life for a sip of this!
Slow down. Chew your food.
\<chew> \<chew> \<burp>
\<gulp>
Mrrrn...
Mrrrn, mrrrn!
Mrm... Mrm...
Mrrrrrrn!
Your weapon in fair shape?
It'll hold.
What do you want?
Stop following me.
Don't you listen?
Go away.
Let's play tag! You're it!
Heh! You can't outrun me!
On three, okay? One...two...
Three!
Hahaha! Slowpoke!
Ugh! No fair!
Go again! This time I'll catch you!
All right! One...two...
Take that!
What was that for!?
Yeah!
Hehe! Feels good, don't it?
I'm soaked!
You'll dry off if you run!
Ugh! Get back here!
Wow, you both run fast!
See? All dry!
\<sigh> Whatever...
That's a good lad...
\<snuffle>
Gathering these took longer than I expected...
Which shop was it again?
A thousand pardons for the wait.
Shopspace must be tidy before boxorders arrive!
Boxorders! Here, here! At the Mobbieshop!
Nonsense, nonsense! Thank you, boxbearer!
I wonder if I'll catch anything here.
Huh? Why are you grasscutting?
Mobbie is making a greengarden to grow all kinds of goodlyplants!
Kweh? Kweh, kweh!
L-Lightning... S-So much lightning...
It used to be dangerous out here, right?
Aye. Thankfully, the barrier protects us from lightning these days.
Without it, there's no way we could come salvaging like this.
Ugh, I was so close...
You'll get it next time, my lord.
“Close,” my arse! He was bloody malms away!
Just watch─I'll master this challenge in no time!
Erm...that's a lot of bombs...
Do be careful, Mistress Tataru!
Now that's some fine scaffolding.
Time to follow the map...
Oooh, it's almost too sparkly to eat!
Glad I could make the trip. It wouldn't be summer without the Moonfire Faire.
Meowww!
Try not to fall, Fhul!
Now where'd my little friend sneak off to...?

Pudding, pudding, firm and cold...♪
Pudding worth its weight in gold...♪
Here, this frozen treat ought to help you cool down.

And the winner is...
this lady!
This festival will surely offer us the inspiration we need for new visions.
The island cries out for chaos, and I intend to deliver.
That's the biggest bug I've ever seen!
Well, Koana has gotten ahead of us now.
I hope Alisaie and Erenville are all right...

That was some fight!
Papa knows how to pick his electors.

Carved histories recreated through magic...
It's an interesting fighting style.
I think I did well considering our opponent!
I've never seen a place like this before.
We must be very deep underground by now.
That light...
Strikingly different from the rest of the cenote...
That was a most unexpected transformation.
Right! Let's get moving!
Now to see what's inside the dome.
He was more snake than man by the end...
It seems the facility is secure.
I'm coming, Zoraal Ja!
To subject people to such heinous experiments...
Let us press on to the summit!
There is no telling what may happen. Let us stay alert.
These precious memories... You would erase them all?
Without her memories, what will Sphene become...?
Well, that was grueling!
W-We won...? We won!
I expected...more.
Small wonder they called it the “Skyruin”!

You fought well, Lamaty'i...
Without hesitation.
I'd been curious to see Zoraal Ja in action...
'Twas an ordeal, indeed.
Brother...
So it is done...
His desire to surpass his father knew neither limit nor reason.
It's finally over...
If only you had found another way...
He has used up all of his souls, as he said he would.
He truly held nothing back...
Sphene...
Don't tell me that was...
Well fought...
\<pant> \<pant>
Then that must be...
What do you want?
Meeeow!
Meow! Meow!
Meeeooow...
Meow...
Meow!♪ Meow!♪
This way, this way!
Where's the support we called for!?
More machines over there!
We won't let them through!
My alpacas are all ready for the road!
Another day in the saddle, my friends.
We're ready to hide in a heartbeat.
Have to stay vigilant at all times.
Still some life left in this.
This is hard work even on the best days.
These should be good for something.
Can barely keep my eyes open...
We can't afford to mope...
I thought I was done for...
Cahciua...
Now to upload the blueprints...
Now where were those weapon blueprints?
Need to expedite the relief supplies...
Right, what needs making next?
This device is for etching circuits on electrope.
I can't believe this is happening...
For now, we just have to do what we can...
Supplies... Have to make supplies...
Oh, you want to play?
Ack! Ugh, you didn't have to spit on me!

I didn't do nothin'! Please,
you gotta let me out!

I-I got a kid at home.
They need me!
Quiet in there!

And enough with the games.
We know you have no family.
Dammit! How did you know?
What are you after today?
I'm looking for an air-wheeler A9. Have you got any...er...smaller sizes?
I mean, this is definitely the convenient choice, but...
Just look at those sleek lines...
I reckon I'll buy a new work desk.
You may as well get a new chair while you're at it!
What's your recommendation?
I know exactly what you mean!
This coffee tastes so much better than the stuff I make at home...
Ahh, this is the life.
Our latest seasonal juice, of course! Care to try it?
These cups are so handy!
Right? The electrope lining keeps your drink at the perfect temperature!
Let's see... What's in today's news?
And then I nearly drove the hover cargo into the damned wall!
Idiot! What would've happened to the company if you crashed!?
Feeling brave enough to go for a walk, pretty bird?
To make up for it, you can buy the coffees!
Erm, I wanted to ask about your policy on distributing soul cells.
Gods, I'm bored...
Gotta be somethin' to do around here.
I'm pretty sure this is the right address...
What's wrong with that feller?
Looks like someone's gotten 'emselves lost.
Oi, you there.
Y-Yes? Wh-What is it?
Get yerself over 'ere. We'll sort you out!
Aaagh! N-No thank you!
Bwahaha! You gone and scared 'im off!
Clearly got the wrong end of the stick...
Th-Those ruffians!
Gods, these things are so slow.
I'll explain the rules...
Easy now, gotta make this look natural.
Wait, is this even where we were supposed to meet?
He's usually so punctual...
H-Hey, handsome! Yeah, you!
You again? What is it this time?

F-Fancy going for a ride?
Just the two of us?
Nah, already got plans. Sorry.
\<sigh> Maybe I need to change my approach?
Sorry I'm late. That girl was...err...asking for directions.
That's not what it looked like from here...
Listen carefully.
Hmmm. Fascinating.
The stars are with you! May your life shine just as brightly!
Goodness gracious. I've never seen anything quite like it.
Alas, the signs are rather dire. You must make efforts to lead a life of temperance.
Wh-What do you mean!?
Oho! What a relief! I wasn't expecting to hear that.
And that's a good thing, right!?
Gods...
Now we wait until it's time to depart.
I'm not sure all these will fit...
How can I possibly get everything done before the deadline?

I can barely think straight...
Not even the coffee's helping.
Sweet, sweet coffee.
Gotta stay limber!
Where is he?
There you are!
Sorry, I lost track of time!
Let's watch the footage of that Arcadion match!
So, what do you fancy doing?
Come to think of it, I haven't seen him in a while.
Ohoho, look who it is! How are you faring?
He's always so busy, right?
Long time no see!
No complaints. I've been flat out at work, though.
You got injured at work?
Oh, it was just a scratch! Besides, as a hunter, it kind of comes with the territory.
Thought I might buy some new clothes─refresh my wardrobe a little.
Well, I for one wouldn't say no to a shopping trip!
Things have gotten a little fraught at work lately...
Managing the expectations of a whole team can be tricky, indeed.
You can't beat a good, old-fashioned stroll in the park!

Maybe I'll just take the rest of the <If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),12))><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),4))>evening<Else/>morning</If><Else/><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),17))>day<Else/>evening</If></If> off!
Ahh. My little fishy wishies are looking as gorgeous as ever!
That clown was amazing!
Turning a pumpkin into a little pup? Whatever will they do next!?
Woof, woof!
What a pretty stone! I bet it's worth a gil or two!
Which way was it? Left, I think...
Better have a look about...
Are those buildings abandoned?
